{"about_the_game":"Get ready to plunge into chaos with Wigged Out, the wackiest, most historically inaccurate ball game ever! <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/ENG_Banner_1_Wig_Flinging_Frenzy_NT_s2.png?t=1739535160\" /> <br><br>Join the wig flinging frenzy in Wigged Out! Toss your wig or other crazy items at opponents and collect an impressive assortment of wigs. Show off your wig-wielding skills!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/GIF_1_Transparent_Custom.gif?t=1739535160\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/ENG_Banner_2_Stay_on_High_Alert_NT_s2.png?t=1739535160\" /><br><br>It's like dodgeball, but on an adrenaline-fueled rollercoaster with ludicrousness. Brace yourself for a showdown against your rival school in this epic battle of balls, where the goal is to wrestle a gigantic ball into your rival's territory, and trust us, there are no rules in this playbook!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/GIF_2_NOTITLE_Transparent_Hazard_.gif?t=1739535160\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/ENG_Banner_3_Unleash_your_WigOut_power_NT_s2.png?t=1739535160\" /><br><br>Forget about the traditional methods of kicking, pushing, or throwing the Big Ball. In Wigged Out, it's all about scavenging for whatever random item you can get your hands on to set that behemoth in motion. And here's the kicker \u2013 if you accidentally miss the Big Ball, you'll discover that these items have a surprising talent for turning your opponents into human pinballs!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/GIF_3_NOTITLE_Transparent_Wigout.gif?t=1739535160\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/ENG_Banner_4_Conquer_80+_levels_NT_s1.png?t=1739535160\" /><br><br>Picture this: send your foes soaring through the air with a perfectly timed explosive keg or give them a slapstick surprise with a rubber turkey to the face. These are just a taste of the hilariously wild strategies you can unleash in a match of Wigged Out. It's a no-holds-barred, anything-goes, laugh-until-your-wig-falls-off kind of game. Grab your quirkiest friends, and let's get this ball rolling!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/GIF_4_NOTITLE_Transparent_Variation.gif?t=1739535160\" /><br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/ENG_Banner_5_Unleash_Hilarity_NT_s2.png?t=1739535160\" /><br><br>Play locally or online for non-stop fun. Add bots and banish loneliness!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/GIF_5_NOTITLE_Transparent_LocalAndOnlineLoop.gif?t=1739535160\" /><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>&quot;WIG FLINGING FRENZY\u201d -</strong> Join the wig flinging frenzy in Wigged Out! Toss your wig or other crazy items at opponents and collect an impressive assortment of wigs. Show off your wig-wielding skills!&quot;<br></li><li><strong>STAY ON HIGH ALERT! \u2013</strong> It's not just opponents you face. Beware of bursting hydrants, rogue manholes, and even a rampaging school mascot goat! Danger lurks at every turn.<br></li><li><strong>UNLEASH YOUR WIGOUT POWER! \u2013</strong> Reach full capacity with stunning plays and witness the magic unfold. Activate your character's extraordinary talent and unleash chaos on the pitch!<br></li><li><strong>CONQUER 80+ LEVELS! \u2013</strong>Explore colorful themes, tackle diverse challenges and enjoy the different sets of items, hazards and goal types!<br></li><li><strong>UNLEASH HILARITY! \u2013</strong> Play locally or online for non-stop fun. Add bots and banish loneliness!</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Well, Hello There","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1176060/53eaa06a57e5fb6bcc0c772a35680bf158c02255.jpg"},{"name":"Gooooal","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1176060/10f3e66bc7396add8e5336b048eaa95d589ac950.jpg"},{"name":"Collector","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1176060/9905025aaf2eb5b5b57864b4713317d91a3a3814.jpg"},{"name":"Goooooooals","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1176060/34ba5fed4b825fee0fb8042e1f3d5ee09899d217.jpg"},{"name":"Rookie","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1176060/0d92efb7c959e03843d1f4a527a76205fde44f99.jpg"},{"name":"Veteran","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1176060/58938a8e7260333b2d7e2a2e3ce0632cd3bcc5b9.jpg"},{"name":"Beginner's Luck","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1176060/15afce84d22a5e7f152de0295a2a58d0568e26f4.jpg"},{"name":"Champion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1176060/06367576bafe998354ae76ff965d3fe498007340.jpg"},{"name":"Goal In One","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1176060/6924dcec998dd9ca9a841ed08671bd07f0dd4e0c.jpg"},{"name":"Wig-Trick","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1176060/7c5198398103be3b993083b7f9db6ddb518f9186.jpg"}],"total":28},"background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1176060?t=1739535160","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_ass